text: Canandaigua (UtaʼnaráhkhwaʼRudes, B. Tuscarora English Dictionary Toronto: University of Toronto Press, 1999 in Tuscarora) is a city in Ontario County, New York, United States. The population was 10,576 at the 2020 census. It is the county seat of Ontario County.Google Maps (3019 County Complex Drive, Canandaigua, New York), Retrieved Jan. 14, 2015.Ontario County, New York, Retrieved Jan. 14, 2015. ==References== Category:Cities in New York (state) Category:County seats in New York (state)
